full_text:
Random thought.

It's crazy how the Jimmy Garropolo market completely dried up after his shoulder surgery. 

He's just sitting on the 49ers roster.

Andrew Booth is a solid CB that not many people are talking about. 

Projected as a late-first rounder, he has a feisty competitiveness I like. 

He's not afraid to initiate contact or support in the run. Also has some sticky hands.
